243
00:13:02,249 --> 00:13:04,249
Dasar anak bodoh!

244
00:13:05,719 --> 00:13:06,820
Maafkan aku, Ayah.

245
00:13:11,420 --> 00:13:12,489
Baik.

246
00:13:13,829 --> 00:13:15,459
Tapi jangan biarkan ibumu tahu.

247
00:13:16,530 --> 00:13:18,229
Begitu dia tahu,

248
00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:20,700
