00:46:36,899 --> 00:46:37,960
Percayalah

784
00:46:38,700 --> 00:46:40,970
saat kakek bilang akan menyelamatkanmu.

785
00:46:41,970 --> 00:46:43,399
Kamu mengerti?

786
00:46:45,069 --> 00:46:46,309
Kakek...

